{"title":"岷江诗钞","authors":["邓林"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"岷江诗钞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修马路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈开悬岩陡壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来修一条马路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头在坝址东边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尾在白云深处。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用女娲五彩石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不借沉香劈山斧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不请二郎担山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕神仙嫉妒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢钎起落闪银光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊走含花野鹿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声炮响开天门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震落辰星无数！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快刀斩断青山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云飞来填补，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松枝结满露珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葛藤牵上栏杆柱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马路是根纽带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"系住风钻和蓝图；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展开图卷起风雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扭动风钻生烟雾！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江水奔腾似箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马路伸延神速。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让器材顺着马路流来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让电力沿着岷江送去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"架铁索桥水上鹅毛浮不起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔江何止隔千里？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸人家不通婚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年共饮江中水！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上银河也有桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上华山也有路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾恶浪扑沙滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惟有岷江不可渡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那有大河不可渡？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那有高山打不开？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山大河只向古人关铁锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今朝且看我们来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党把铁锤交给了我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥动铁锤开铁锁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲熔化白头山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山旗帜红于火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野水嚎啕北斗高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢绳缚住孽龙腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"败鳞残甲铺成路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打扫云雾架飞桥！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"责令鳌鱼背桥墩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不准鳌鱼眨眼睛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此岷江歌声更嘹亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拦河横挂七弦琴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南岸人家拍手笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北岸人家心直跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片欢呼万朵花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽车开过桥来了！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}